PrecisOrder (a) approving a SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between the Crown and the KWAKIUTL BAND which will compensate them for the loss of Tsulquate Indian Reserve No. 4, and (b) setting apart, for their use and benefit, some 260 acres of land ("The Walden Property") located in rural British Columbia, as Walden Indian Reserve No. 9.
